CHANGES
=======

10.6.2
------

* Removing debug output of 51-hosts
* Cleanup stale interface if exists
* Disable yum-plugin-priorities elements for CentOS8

10.6.1
------

* Update TOX/UPPER\_CONSTRAINTS\_FILE for stable/train
* Update .gitreview for stable/train

10.6.0
------

* Sync Sphinx requirement
* Update the constraints url

10.5.1
------

* Clear net.ifnames definition
* Fix line comparisons
* Add Python 3 Train unit tests

10.5.0
------

* Replace multinode jobs with image builds
* Replace git.openstack.org URLs with opendev.org URLs
* Remove note in README regarding security hardened images
* OpenDev Migration Patch
* Update master for stable/stein
* [Documentation] Migrate the format

10.4.0
------

* Replace openstack.org git:// URLs with https://

10.3.0
------

* Update hacking version

10.2.0
------

* [Configuration] Add missing py37 and corrected default envlist
* [Configuration] Update min tox version
* Drop baremetal job template
* Change openstack-dev to openstack-discuss
* Install rsync before os-apply-config
* Optimizing the safety of the http link site in HACKING.rst
* Update min tox version to 2.0

10.1.0
------

* Increase size for security hardened images
* fix tox python3 overrides

10.0.0
------

* add python 3.6 unit test job
* add python 3.5 unit test job
* Fix unit tests in python3
* Update reno for stable/rocky
* switch documentation job to new PTI
* import zuul job settings from project-config

9.0.0
-----


9.0.0.0b3
---------

* Add release note link in README
* Add overcloud-secure-uefi element
* Update links in README

9.0.0.0b2
---------

* Fix readme formating issues
* Add python jobs to tripleo-image-elements
* Add a 60 seconds timeout to ping\_metadata\_ip()
* remove os-cloud-config element

9.0.0.0b1
---------

* Add a dependency on block-device-mbr element
* Increase the image size to 23G
* Update reno for stable/queens

8.0.0.0rc1
----------

* Zuul: Remove project name
* Add another path for service files
* Zuul: Remove project name

8.0.0.0b3
---------

* Remove RH1 OVB jobs from configuration
* Make sure, the realtime element removes the default kernel
* Add realtime-kernel element
* Adding mapping for SUSE package

8.0.0.0b2
---------

* Remove unused tox\_install.sh
* Migrate t-i-e to zuul v3 jobs
* Exclude 'vnet' interfaces from being candidates for running a dhcp client
* Use volumes for security hardened images

8.0.0.0b1
---------

* Add missing target\_core\_mod to iscsi modules
* Change After rule from cloud-final to cloud-config
* Update ironic-agent-multipath element
* Use Python to compute release notes version
* Update reno for stable/pike

7.0.0.0rc1
----------

* Prepare reno for TripleO Pike RC1
* Create symlink for dib-run-parts

7.0.0.0b3
